title: Origami to Astonish and Amuse, by Jeremy Shafer.pdf
description:
This is one of my all time favorite origami books!  It's written by an extremely talented Jeremy Shafer, who is a bay area local.  He's even taught origami at Camp Winnarainbow, which I personally went to as a kid.

I'm sorry, but a hair got on the scanner bed (unnoticed until after the job was done), and some of the corners were bent/folded on some of the scans.  When I went back to the original book to re-scan the fucked up pages, I found the book was damaged (waterlogged), preventing from getting a better 2nd scan.  Thank God I've got the book backed up on my computer now ;-)

Enjoy
